<br>
Heres a step by step guide to nerfing twinking though...<br>
<br>
Write a script to search the item database and edit it.<br>
<br>
1. All haste items can have a hard level limit of haste percentage +10 levels.  FBSS is limited to 30 COF to 46.<br>
<br>
2. All weapons can be hard capped based on ratio.<br>
<br>
3. All regen items can be capped at 51.<br>
<br>
4. Make it so that players getting healed buffed mid fight by a player 20 levels higher get no exp.<br>
<br>
