<br>
When *I* say mana potion, I mean *click* and I get half a bar of mana or more.  Only works outside a fight.  Might take all of 30 seconds to fill it that far, and would be cancelled if I stand up, get hit, etc...  If they tracked 'in combat' like DAOC, it would stop if anyone in my party got in a fight, as any member entering combat makes the whole group considered in combat-- hell, even pets will defend a groupmate in trouble regardless if the person getting hit is the pet caster. <p><br>
